SABMiller’s Castle Lager Becomes Lead Sponsor of South African Rugby Team

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-11T10:39:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/sabmiller-s-castle-lager-becomes-lead-sponsor-of-south-african-rugby-team.html
SABMiller Plc (SAB) ’s Castle Lager brand
will become the new title sponsor for the southern hemisphere’s
Tri-Nations rugby union tournament between  South Africa ,  New
Zealand  and  Australia , the South African Rugby Union said in an
e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  